###  https://hyberion.example/ontology/se/RoboticSystem#RoboticSystem
:RoboticSystem rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000040> ;
               <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A material entity that is an engineering system which is designed to perform automated physical tasks in a designated operational environment." .


###  https://hyberion.example/ontology/se/RoboticSystem#SystemOperationProcess
:SystemOperationProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                        rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> ;
                        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A process during which an engineering system is actively deployed to realise its designated function in a specific operational environment." .


###  https://hyberion.example/ontology/se/RoboticSystem#Systemfunction
:Systemfunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000034> ;
                <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A function that inheres in an engineering system and the realisation of which constitutes the system's designated operational role." .


